description:
I wasn't really sure I wanted to start the New Year with a video of me, but during these marathons I will fill in some days with videos I may not otherwise air. ~ahem!
This video wasn't just about me fucking Jamison, but training Travis to film. If I am gonna do a mini-series of these, I may not want to rely on tripods and POV shots.
Not gonna go into much detail on this one. I will let the peanut gallery have at it.
I know I have some fans who joined ChaosMen to see me interact a little bit more with the models. So this one is for you, and for those that don't appreciate it, I hope you enjoyed all the other videos in this marathon!
title: Bryan & Jamison - RAW
